      <h2>
        <span id="hs_cos_wrapper_name" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_meta_field hs_cos_wrapper_type_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="meta_field"
          data-hs-cos-type="text">A Primer for the Torchbearer RPG</span>
      </h2>
      <div id="hubspot-author_data" class="hubspot-editable post__author" data-hubspot-form-id="author_data" data-hubspot-name="Blog Author"><a
          href="//blog.mordite.press/author/lord-mordeth" class="post__author-avatar">
          <img class="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-src="https://cdn2.hubspot.net/hub/2068068/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202018-08-19%20at%2012.14.57%20PM.png?width=70&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202018-08-19%20at%2012.14.57%20PM.png"
